Subject: [PATCH] Pin Chromium GPU producers and syncobj to the Wayland device

# Shared Chromium GPU-selection patch. Wayland's DMA-BUF main_device selects
# Dawn, native Vulkan, ANGLE, GBM, VA-API, and browser-process syncobj ioctls.
